Class CareProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.cmput301f18t11.medicam.models.abstracts.PersistedModel
      • ca.ualberta.cmput301f18t11.medicam.models.abstracts.User
        • ca.ualberta.cmput301f18t11.medicam.models.CareProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class CareProvider
extends User
    Represents a careprovider user account that holds a list of patients that are tracked by/assigned to this careprovider.

    The patients associated with this CareProvider object are represented by a List of String type uuids that uniquely identify each Patient.
